s://github.com/directus/directus/discussions/categories/q-a\">Community Help Board</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/DirectusVideos/featured\">Video Tutorials on YouTube</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/directus-community\">Community Repositories</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community-resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community-resources\" aria-label=\"community resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community Resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/DirectusBR\">Portuguese YouTube Channel</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"integration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#integration\" aria-label=\"integration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Integration</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@directus/sdk\">Offical JS SDK</a> - The JS SDK provides an intuitive interface for the Directus API from within a JavaScript-powered project (Browsers and Node.js).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@directus/gatsby-source-directus\">Offical Gatsby Source Plugin</a> - Source plugin for pulling data into Gatsby from a Directus API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gremo/react-directus\">react-directus</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/gremo/react-directus\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">39</span></span></a> - A set of React components and utilities for Directus Headless CMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pub.dev/packages/directus\">Flutter SDK</a> - Flutter SDK to provide interface for Directus API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/alantiller/directus-php-sdk\">PHP SDK</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/alantiller/directus-php-sdk\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">19</span></span></a> - PHP SDK to provide easy access to the Directus API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jacoborus/directus-lite-sdk\">Lite SDK (TypeScript)</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jacoborus/directus-lite-sdk\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">9</span></span></a> - Query builder for the Directus API (Browser, Deno, Node.js). Bring your own fetch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nuxtus.com\">Nuxtus</a> - Provides a Nuxt boilerplate and set of tools to automatically create Nuxt pages from Directus Collections.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"extensions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#extensions\" aria-label=\"extensions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Extensions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/resauce-dev/directus-image-scout?ref=awesome-directus\">Image Scout</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/resauce-dev/directus-image-scout\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">66</span></span></a> - Search and select images found on a variety of royalty free image sites (Pexels, Pixabay, Unsplash &#x26; Giphy!).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-editorjs-interface\">Editor.js Interface</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-editorjs-interface\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">122</span></span></a> - Block editor (Editor.js) interface for Directus 9.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jesusgp22/directus-draw-interface\">Draw Interface</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jesusgp22/directus-draw-interface\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7</span></span></a> - Free draw interface for Directus app.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ToJans/fa18e2a7363edd24be6ad8dda2dd0232\">User-friendly file paths</a> - Use the folder and file module structure to reference to assets.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/u12206050/directus-9-date-picker-interface\">Date Picker Interface</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/u12206050/directus-9-date-picker-interface\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px