key-value pairs as JSON blobs with a progress indicator for completeness.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-wpslug-interface\">WordPress-like Slug</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-wpslug-interface\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">45</span></span></a> - Slug/Permalink interface with support for pre- and suffixes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-linkmeta\">Link Meta</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-linkmeta\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">16</span></span></a> - Stores hyperlink metadata into Directus.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-group-modal-interface\">Group Modal</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dimitrov-adrian/directus-extension-group-modal-interface\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, 